1) ChangeLogs based on library
https://github.com/gabrielemariotti/changeloglib

2) How it works
* content of change log is described in file res/raw/changelog.xml

a) If you want to add bold text, use next
<changelogtext>[b]This is bold text[/b] Normal text.</changelogtext>

b) Add link.
<changelogimprovement><![CDATA[Text before link <a href="http://www.google.it">manual</a> and after link]]></changelogimprovement>

c) italic text:
<changelogtext>Normal text [i]italic text[/i]</changelogtext>

d) about bug
<changelogbug>Fixed a [a href="http://www.google.it"]number[/a] of bugs with the Gmail and SMS extensions</changelogbug>
